{"tid":2274713,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭月娥：香港不會因經濟理由不理中國人民健康","createTime":"2020-11-06T15:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T05:44:50.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"7f4998c0c3682d8d5550003837ecc426887fe5d1","tid":2274713,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:16:29.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥總結訪京之行。她說，已向中央反映香港各界對早日免除兩地人員14日檢疫，有強烈訴求，但香港的抗疫防疫要做得更嚴格，今天不能講何時做到有關目標。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥回應內地傳媒問到，內地很多反對放寬豁免14天檢疫安排的聲音，她回應，現時中港兩地需要14天檢疫安排，是為老百姓健康而設，兩地政府必須要在保障人民健康的前提下，才會解除14天檢疫的安排，香港不會因為經濟理由，隨便回應香港居民的訴求，不理會內地人民的健康，希望內地居民放心。"},{"pid":"c4b2d7a86df6a595ffd519518190a8cd968b8563","tid":2274713,"uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:16:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558768-20201106.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558768-20201106.htm&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9kUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=982c12e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558768-20201106.htm&h=4644320f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558768-20201106.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6d60194cf269d91d7fa267f0e776c215841d8727","tid":2274713,"uid":363468,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:22:08.000Z","msg":"佢無講錯, 係為中國人民健康, 唔係香港人呀!!!"},{"pid":"b47ab9a62d8fce82d7436bbe16470048ba426d37","tid":2274713,"uid":54721,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:32:49.000Z","msg":"唔好開阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdc1753634d7588475984b010f75f22f9c12dab5","tid":2274713,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:33:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5d1717ac56836155bb439f49152ae42ff818e0","tid":2274713,"